net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser

Class BasicCsvLineParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser.BaseCsvLineParser
      • net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser.BasicCsvLineParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICsvByteLineParser, ICsvCharLineParser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicCsvLineParserExtended

    public class BasicCsvLineParser
extends BaseCsvLineParser
    Basic CSV line parser. Basically - If the Field start with {Quote}; the fields is ended by {Quote}{Field-Seperator} - Otherwise the field ends with a {Field-Separator}
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
